These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
City: boston, hannover
Beverage: hot-chocolate, milk
Hobby: rock-climbing, hiking
Job: librarian, coach
Game: go, chess
1. Hobby:hiking is on the right of City:boston##1
2. Job:coach is on the far left##1
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
4. Game:chess is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| City   | boston     | hannover     |
| Beverage   | milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | hiking  |
| Job           | coach    | librarian |
| Game         | chess   | go       |

