.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
City: edinburgh, san-francisco
House: futuristic, craftsman
Cigar: pall-mall, game
Color: grey, lilac
Game: mah-jongg, monopoly
1. City:edinburgh is on the right of Color:grey##1
2. Cigar:pall-mall == House:futuristic##1
3. Cigar:pall-mall is in an even position##4
4. House:craftsman is on the left or right of Game:mah-jongg##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| City      | san-francisco    | edinburgh |
| House           | craftsman  | futuristic     |
| Cigar   | game       | pall-mall      |
| Color           | grey        | lilac      |
| Game         | monopoly | mah-jongg     |

